location.fullValue: Larimar Plan, Parkside at Gladden Farms

data.description: VA Buyers Ask About VA ASSUMABLE @ approx 2.375% APR! Beautiful former Richmond Model home the ''Sapphire'' plan. Featuring 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms with a full separate living/den area. A well appointed kitchen with stainless appliances flows into the dining and living area. Two separate bedrooms in front of home with shared full bathroom in between. This home has a large owner's suite with all the upgrades and beautifully tiled shower. Two walk in closets highlight the Primary bedroom. Tile floors throughout all living areas except bedrooms.  Kitchen features upgraded lighting, and full back splash with black hardware and a large open island for entertaining. Mountain views to the East facing Backyard which is complete with turf and fire pit! Call for a showing!
